WEBVTT

02:17:29.358 --> 02:17:30.733
You were deceiving me,
weren't you?

02:17:30.733 --> 02:17:31.983
What are you talking about?

02:17:32.024 --> 02:17:33.024
What happened?

02:17:33.274 --> 02:17:34.899
-Tell me what's going on, Bastin.
-Where's Sahadevan?

02:17:34.941 --> 02:17:36.566
He's not here. He's staying
at another house nearby.
